  "code": "%% Stand-up Meeting Reality by emphonic.com\n%% The daily scrum experience of every developer\n\njourney\n    title Daily Stand-up Meeting Reality\n    section Before Stand-up\n      Check Slack for fires: 2: Dev\n      Pretend to remember yesterday: 1: Dev\n      Make coffee: 5: Dev\n    section The Stand-up\n      Say worked on same ticket: 3: Dev\n      Mention blockers no one fixes: 2: Dev\n      Hear PM add urgent feature: 1: Dev, PM\n      Watch 15-min meeting hit 45-min: 1: Everyone\n    section After Stand-up\n      Actually start working: 4: Dev\n      Get pulled into another meeting: 1: Dev\n      Debug why prod is down: 1: Dev, Ops\n",
